name: Abnormal temperator refrigerator
one_liner: A refrigerator that will keep the contents at a higher/lower than normal temperature (65-70F) using a deep freeze freezer.
product_tags_string: Environmental Sensing, Internet Of Things, Smart appliances
hproperties: "story_json"=>"[{\"type\":\"CE\",\"hash\":\"pn8l\",\"json\":[{\"tag\":\"p\",\"content\":null,\"attribs\":{},\"children\":[{\"tag\":\"span\",\"content\":\"I need to keep a refrigerator at a constant temperature of about 65-70 degrees Fahrenheit that can be adjusted to a lower temperature if needed for some beer brewing. The plan is to use a deep freeze freezer due to the insulation and ability to easily cool to a lower temperature when needed.
